- TRY ONE OF THESE,
MONSIEUR.

38:40.852 --> 38:42.421
- OH, NO, NO, I COULDN'T.

38:42.454 --> 38:44.856
- SURE YOU CAN-CAN.
- [chuckles]

38:44.890 --> 38:46.792
- [laughs]

38:49.461 --> 38:50.862
- THIS IS AMAZING.

38:50.896 --> 38:52.831
I CANNOT BELIEVE
WHAT EMMETT ACCOMPLISHED.

38:52.864 --> 38:55.133
- WELL, HE'S BEEN WORKING
LIKE A DOG--

38:55.166 --> 38:57.969
