GOING TO COST ME?

39:07.145 --> 39:08.580
- YOU'LL BE HAPPY
TO KNOW THAT

39:08.614 --> 39:11.116
EMMETT IS VERY RESOURCEFUL.

39:11.149 --> 39:15.654
- MMM, THEN BOOK HIM FOR
THE SURREALIST SHOW IN JUNE.

39:15.687 --> 39:19.391
