HE'S GOING TO BE BUSY.

39:19.425 --> 39:23.729
- [chuckles]
- EXCUSE ME.

39:23.762 --> 39:25.997
- I FEEL LIKE THE TOWN SLUT
ON PROM NIGHT.

39:26.031 --> 39:27.399
[chuckles]
AGAIN!

39:27.433 --> 39:28.900
[laughs]

39:28.934 --> 39:31.069
LOOK AT ALL THESE CARDS.
- WOW.

39:31.102 --> 39:32.671
- I'M PROUD OF YOU, EM.

39:32.704 --> 39:35.140
- OH, THANKS, BABY.
- CAREFUL ON THE BACK.

39:35.173 --> 39:36.775
- OH, SORRY.

39:36.808 --> 39:38.477
