THE PASTRIES?

39:39.778 --> 39:41.046
- YOU'RE THE PLANNER.

39:41.079 --> 39:43.882
- WELL, THEN I SAY,
FOLLOW ME, TROOPS.

39:43.915 --> 39:48.153
IT'S TIME THOSE NAPOLEONS
MET THEIR WATERLOO!

39:48.186 --> 39:50.522
- I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.
- OKAY.

39:52.791 --> 39:55.527
